    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于游戏： </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--  建造  --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你可以收集资源，并用于建造你的城堡和房屋，来抵御敌人的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/a6d417f01f4c64e31070cd5ed5544124.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/a6d417f01f4c64e31070cd5ed5544124.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/a6d417f01f4c64e31070cd5ed5544124.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--  战斗  --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天夜里都有敌人的巡逻队，准备拿起你的武器迎敌吧。击败敌人，并找回被它们抢走的建筑图纸，解锁更多建筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ee9eff081dc52f4442f53e8077b2da0a.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ee9eff081dc52f4442f53e8077b2da0a.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ee9eff081dc52f4442f53e8077b2da0a.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--  捕获敌人  --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的，除了战斗之外，我们还可以抓捕它们，让他们为你工作。除此之外，我们还可以收买其它生物来帮助我们战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ec938e4e4e394dad932a9509e9b399ec.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ec938e4e4e394dad932a9509e9b399ec.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/ec938e4e4e394dad932a9509e9b399ec.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--  团队作战  --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以给其它村民发号施令，让他们发挥自己的特长，更好的配合你的行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/fc164308a8095fc082e058c0a9fb65e4.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/fc164308a8095fc082e058c0a9fb65e4.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/fc164308a8095fc082e058c0a9fb65e4.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--  昼夜系统  --</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该如何安排你每天的时间，如何进行决策，完全取决于你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.poster.avif?t=1748216418\" width=568 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.webm?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277250/extras/c087a45da1118babbe07f07bcb08b35a.mp4?t=1748216418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集，战斗，探索，建造！在这个动感十足的冒险游戏里没有什么是不可能的。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起你的工具出发！与敌人作战，在黑夜里活下去。收集资源创造你的世界所需要的一切。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终打败黑暗势力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要注意，那有很多挑战在等着你……你能完成任务吗？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
